= Locations =

'''Dragon Warrior III''' (NES) features a world based on real Earth geography, with locations across multiple continents.

__TOC__

== World Overview ==

The game takes place in two worlds:
* '''Upper World''' - Main world based on real Earth
* '''Alefgard''' - Underground world (setting of DW1)

